<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:4:63">
	Join our Red Shield Youth Centers&nbsp;for an action-packed summer&nbsp;program, with steam activities, games, arts &amp; crafts, outdoor play, engaging programs and field trips. Daily snacks are provided. And scholarship opportunities&nbsp;are available.
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:5:41"><strong>June 15-August 14</strong></p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:6:37">(Closed on June 19&nbsp;and the week of June 29-July 3)</p>
<h6 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:7:25">Registration</h6>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:8:66"><strong>Weekly Fees - $80 per week/child&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:9:16">Weekly fees are $80&nbsp;and should be paid Friday prior to the week of attendance. The program is first come first serve; we will not secure a spot on the roster until your payment is received.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:10:11"><strong>Camp T-shirt&nbsp;Fee&nbsp;- $12</strong></p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:11:46">Summer Day Camp t-shirt fees should be paid prior to the first week of attendance.</p>
