<h4 style="text-align:center;">Red Shield Summer Adventures</h4>

<p style="text-align:center;">
	Make this summer unforgettable for our Red Shield Youth Center kids by providing fun-filled outings, during Summer Day Camp.
</p>

<p style="text-align:center;" class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-center"><a href="https://give.salvationarmycarolinas.org/campaign/782128/donate" class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2">Give Today!</a></p></div>
				</div>
			</div>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:21:40"></div>
<div class="row g-3 my-3 align-items-stretch" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:22:5">
<div class="col-12 d-flex flex-column" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:22:5-1:1 column - 1 row:0">
<div class="card-wysiwyg-body d-flex flex-column h-100 w-100 flex-fill rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-light text-dark card-outline border border-secondary-subtle" style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:20:17"><p>
	<img class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/001c2a47-75b4-46ee-8bba-6ec5b1eb7f03_Red+Shield+Youth+Centers+Logo+-+Color+-+1500x338.png">
</p>

<p style="text-align:center;">
	The Salvation Army’s high-quality after-school programs, at our Red Shield Youth Centers, serve children and youth of all ages. Our staff and volunteers&nbsp;provide one-on-one assistance with homework and school assignments, as well as the teaching and advancement of literacy and study skills. Our no-fee or low-cost after-school programs offer children&nbsp;a chance to play sports, learn athletic skills, and cultivate healthy, safe relationships with friends through better social skills.
</p>

<p style="text-align:center;">
	<iframe allow="encrypted-media" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" mozallowfullscreen="" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jCixIOxLrRc" webkitallowfullscreen="" width="560"></iframe>
</p></div>
				</div>
			</div>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:24:96"></div>
<div class="row g-3 my-3 align-items-stretch" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:25:9">
<div class="col-12 d-flex flex-column" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:25:9-1:1 column - 1 row:0">
<div class="card-wysiwyg-body d-flex flex-column h-100 w-100 flex-fill rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-primary-200 text-light" style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:23:46"><h5><iframe allow="encrypted-media" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" mozallowfullscreen="" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hzB-6OqlPZg" webkitallowfullscreen="" width="560"></iframe></h5>

<h5 style="text-align:center;">The Salvation Army School of&nbsp;Performing Arts</h5>

<p style="text-align:center;">
	As part of the <a href="https://southernusa.salvationarmy.org/carolinas-music-and-arts/home" target=""><span style="color:#ffffff;">Carolinas Music &amp; Arts Department</span></a>, our School of&nbsp;Performing Arts (SPA)<span style="color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#ffffff;">program</span>&nbsp;enables children and youth to experience music and art education in a&nbsp;positive no-cost or low-cost environment. Our wide array of classes focuses on everything from choir, band, and dancing to drawing, writing, and acting, instilling an early love and appreciation of the fine arts.
</p>

<p style="text-align:center;" class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-center"><a href="mailto:rebecca.mcgee@uss.salvationarmy.org" target="_new" class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2">Contact Us for More Information</a></p></div>
